# extensions

- uBlock Origin
- NoScript
	- [*] temporarily set top-level sitez to TRUSTED
- Vimium C - All By Keyboard
- KeePassXC-Browser
- FoxyProxy
	- setup SOCKS 5 proxy on local host with .ssh/config

# Einstellungen
## about:prefenrences
appearance: dark
Downloads: always ask

### home
use firefox home on homepage, new windows and tabs
deactivate all home content

### search
- default search engine:
	- url: https://noai.duckduckgo.com/
	- POST data:
		- q=%s         ; search query
		- kg=p         ; use post request for future searches
		- kc=-1        ; infinite scroll images: off
		- kav=-1       ; infinite scroll: off
		- kz=-1        ; short summary: off
		- kaj=m        ; units: metric
		- kj=7750AA    ; header color
		- k7=222222    ; background color
		- kae=d        ; darkmode
		- s=s          ; text size: small
	- unused:
		- kbg=-1       ; duck.ai: off, already provided by noai.ddg
		- kbe=0        ; search assist: never, already provided by noai.ddg
		- kbj=1        ; hide-ai images: on, already provided by noai.ddg


### privacy
[*] strict
[*] always use private browsing mode
[*] HTTPS-Only Mode in all windows
[*] DNS over HTTPS
## about:config
privacy.resistFingerprintig    true

### no AI
browser.ml.linkPreview.enabled
browser.ml.chat.enabled
browser.ml.enable
browser.tabs.groups.smart.enabled
browser.tabs.groups.smart.userEnabled
extensions.ml.enabled
sidebar.revamp
